snippet.title: Adobe Premiere Rush with Amber Torrealba - 3 of 3
snippet.description:
Join Amber Torrealba on Adobe Live as she edits a YouTube video for her channel, introducing you to Premiere Rush CC, Adobe’s brand new all-in-one video app! Today, Amber focuses on color correction and her outro.

Amber is a professional skimboarder who captures, edits and produces lifestyle content.

-----

►Check out Amber’s YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/ambertorrealba 
►Click HERE for part 1: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zlxG0ULmav0

Recap: 2:10
Work begins: 3:15 
Editing clip sound to change video mood: 16:45
Adding Titles: 41:50
Adding transitions to titles: 51:00
Exporting to youtube: 57:20
Video orientation for social media: 1:22:35

► Click HERE to watch LIVE: http://bit.ly/AdobeLiveBe
